Quickly Delete Individual Applications

Use the Delete button on individual applications that are a Grantmaking type. Previously, in orgs with Grantmaking enabled users set individual applications to an inactive status. Now, they can delete the records they don’t need.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions where Grantmaking is enabled.
title: Delete Individual Grant Applications
